'''Bell''' is an [[unincorporated community]] in [[Logan County, Illinois|Logan County]], [[Illinois]], [[United States]]. Bell is located on [[Illinois Route 121]] about {{mi to km|2}} north of [[Lincoln, Illinois|Lincoln]].

